author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Panasonic LED bathroom exhaust fan installation tips…This bathroom needed more light and a stronger exhaust fan. I installed the Panasonic WhisperGreen Select for those reasons. The CFM is adjustable and the LED light has 5 different color temperatures, I adjusted mine to match the vanity light color. This fan is a great option to make any bathroom look luxurious. Many thanks to Panasonic for providing this fan for my client’s remodel. Here’s the link to learn more about this exhaust fan https://iaq.na.panasonic.com/next-generation-whispergreen-select 🔥#bathroomremodel #exhaustfans #homerenovation #panasoniciaq #homerepairtutor #brandpartner
